# PKGBUILD Manager — bash script notification keys
# These are symbolic keys resolved at runtime by data/nautilus-scripts/_i18n.
#
# !! ADD new entries here when adding a new bash script operation !!
# Each new operation needs:
#   1. A notify_<name>       entry ("operation started")
#   2. A notify_<name>_ok    entry ("operation succeeded")
#   3. A notify_<name>_fail  entry ("operation failed")
# Then add the English fallback in data/nautilus-scripts/_i18n → _en_fallback()
